description: I still don‘t know what shopping-malls were invented for. Just for shopping or as I suppose for meeting and watching cute guys everywhere? However, today I met someone who you American guys would probably call a „jock“. He just left the gym when I followed him. It was a bit tricky to get his attention as he was about to meet with a friend. But once I start to talk about money they immediately seem to have time. What a strange but funny world. I had to invest a good sum to make him follow me to the toilets. There he showed me his dick. I managed to invite him for a cola afterwards. I had to move on and so I ask him if he would be so kind to take my dick into his mouth:-)
title: Czech Hunter 111
